This are my settings I tend to pull into my work environments.
Most importantly, vim settings to get me productive. :-)

Setup when the home is not empty:
git init .
git remote add origin https://github.com/maettu/Settings.git
git pull origin master

Homedir is empty, simply:
git clone https://github.com/maettu/Settings.git .

xkb:
----
sudo mv /usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/ch /usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/ch-original
sudo ln -s /home/ti/daten/Settings/xkb/ch /usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/ch
sudo rm /var/lib/xkb/*.xkm

(Am besten geht es mit dem Editieren im alt-F1, damit man das File offen lassen kann beim logout-login auf X)
